    "description": {
      "zh": "一款9x18毫米马卡洛夫口径弹药，采用实心钢质平头弹头，表面覆有\"Hi-Tek\"聚合物涂层以减少枪管积垢。这种硬质铸造平头弹属于非扩张型强力穿透弹，专为丛林防卫需求设计。无论是抵御野猪还是黑熊，硬质铸造平头弹均能持续有效地击倒遭遇的各类野生动物。",
      "en": "A 9x18mm Makarov cartridge with a solid steel flat nose bullet coated with \"Hi-Tek\" polymer based coating that reduces fouling in the barrel.  The hard cast flat nose bullet is a non-expanding, powerfully penetrative bullet that is designed with woods defense needs in mind.  Whether fending off wild hogs or black bears, the hard cast flat nose bullets are consistently effective in taking down any encountered wild animals."
    },
